title: Jason Aldean Tells Us He's Done Having Kids + Our Favorite Christmas Songs + How A Listener’s Dog Saved Her Kid From A Bee Attack
itunes:title: Jason Aldean Tells Us He's Done Having Kids + Our Favorite Christmas Songs + How A Listener’s Dog Saved Her Kid From A Bee Attack
description:
Jason Aldean stops by for the release of his new album “9” and talks family, their new house and how he’s done having kids. We go around the room and share our favorite Christmas songs. Bobby talked about a story of a doctor who saved a man’s life on a flight by sucking urine from his bladder.
